44c16419c07597ba6d06d66057fbe2ab86e7b02b5dcdf458678b4ea87f6f721840da951ae4df59c983e1da83abdbe45f82e44a6a311bd42eb94d93dfd5aa437c  irrlicht-1.8.3-mesa-10.x.patch
